{"content": "I need to multiply 456 \u00d7 9a0 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 456 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 456\u2081\u2081 = 4\u00d711\u00b2 + 5\u00d711\u00b9 + 6\u00d711\u2070\n- = 4\u00d7121 + 5\u00d711 + 6\u00d71\n- = 484 + 55 + 6\n- = 545\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 9a0 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 9a0\u2081\u2081 = 9\u00d711\u00b2 + 10\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070\n- = 9\u00d7121 + 10\u00d711 + 0\n- = 1089 + 110 + 0\n- = 1199\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 545 \u00d7 1199 = 653,455\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 653,455 to base 11**\n- 653,455 \u00f7 11 = 59,405 R 0\n- 59,405 \u00f7 11 = 5,400 R 5\n- 5,400 \u00f7 11 = 490 R 10 (a)\n- 490 \u00f7 11 = 44 R 6\n- 44 \u00f7 11 = 4 R 0\n- 4 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 4\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 406a50\n\n406a50", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 365, "completion_tokens": 403}